"This is a wonderful Mocha Stout.  The smell of roasted malts, chocolate and spices makes your mouth water.  The flavor was even better than the aroma.  The taste of deeply roasted malts and a combination of coca, spices and the balance of sweetness and tart, put a wonderful spin on the Mocha Stout.  I'm on my way out to buy more before they run out!"
