"Mouthfeel is really good.  Nice heavy medium feel yet a long lingering flavor.  Well carbonated without being too strong.  A real flavor explosion going on here, but with such a strong flavor it  maintains some smoothness while going to a dry earthiness then ends with a dry finish then some heat lingering afterwards from the peppers.  Nice drinkable beer.  At 8.1% and all that flavor it's still really a beer any stout lover could handle easily.  Another great Stone collaboration.  If this were brewed again I'd definitely get it.  A rare treat."
