"Pours a dark brown almost black color with  a fluffy 3"" head that lasts a long time. Chocolate, coffee, and nutmeg are detectable by the nose. The roasted malt base has a layer of dark chocolate, nutmeg, some hint of cinnamon, and a bit of coffee on top of it. Some pepper arrives late in the taste. Moderate bitterness herer too. Easy to drink beer."
